# TodoMVC Architecture Plan (Leptos + Axum + SQLite)

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: Leptos (SSR + hydration via cargo-leptos)
- Backend: Axum (integrated via leptos_axum)
- Database: SQLite via SQLx with compile-time checked queries
- Build tool: cargo-leptos

