## Data Model
```rust
struct Todo {
    id: i64,
    title: String,
    completed: bool,
    created_at: i64,  // unix timestamp for ordering
}
```

## Server Functions (Issue dependencies)
- `add_todo(title: String) -> Result<Todo>`        # Issue #4
- `list_todos() -> Result<Vec<Todo>>`              # Issue #4
- `toggle_todo(id: i64) -> Result<Todo>`           # Issue #6
- `delete_todo(id: i64) -> Result<()>`             # Issue #7
- `update_todo(id: i64, title: String) -> Result<Todo>`  # Issue #8
- `toggle_all(completed: bool) -> Result<()>`      # Issue #9
- `clear_completed() -> Result<()>`                # Issue #11

