## Key Design Decisions
- Use `RwSignal<Vec<Todo>>` at the App level; pass read/write handles down
- Filter state stored as URL hash (#/ #/active #/completed) via Leptos router
- SQLx pool stored in Axum state, passed to server fns via `use_context`
- Use `leptos::server_fn::error::ServerFnError` for all server fn errors
- TodoMVC canonical CSS loaded via `<Stylesheet>` in the app shell
- `cargo-leptos` handles WASM compilation and asset serving
- Inline editing: double-click sets `editing: Option<i64>` signal, blur/Enter saves
- toggle-all: checked when ALL todos complete; clicking flips all to opposite state
